#, fuzzy
msgid "Why Elasticsearch only?"
msgstr "为什么只用 Elasticsearch？"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hibernate Search supports both a Lucene backend and an Elasticsearch backend."
msgstr "Hibernate Search 同时支持 Lucene 和 Elasticsearch 后端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In the context of Quarkus and to build scalable applications, we thought the latter would make more sense.\n"
"Thus, we focused our efforts on it."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 的背景下，为了构建可扩展的应用程序，我们认为后者更为合理。因此，我们将精力集中在了此处。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.27/guides/hibernate-search-orm-elasticsearch.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We don't have plans to support the Lucene backend in Quarkus for now,\n"
"though there is an issue tracking progress on such an implementation in the Quarkiverse:\n"
"https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras/issues/179[quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras#179]."
msgstr "目前我们尚无计划在 Quarkus 中支持 Lucene 后端，不过 Quarkiverse 上有一个问题跟踪了该实现的进展： link:https://github.com/quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras/issues/179[quarkiverse/quarkus-hibernate-search-extras#179] 。"

